  "detailed_description": "<h1>【CONTINUOUS UPDATES】</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game will constantly add new characters, NPCs, props, gems! If you have any comments on the game, have found bugs and translation errors, please send an email to: <a href=\"mailto:YoungMage@qq.com\">YoungMage@qq.com</a> We will reply to you within 48 hours!</p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928090/extras/0839190d045b5ab84b1f3e1c76571ad4.avif?t=1743991103\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928090/extras/cff9136f41a39f91e10eb7c1371b854b.poster.avif?t=1743991103\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928090/extras/cff9136f41a39f91e10eb7c1371b854b.webm?t=1743991103\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928090/extras/cff9136f41a39f91e10eb7c1371b854b.mp4?t=1743991103\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Dungeon Mercenaries is an endless replayability RPG. Every time you wake up, it's a new start, procedurally generated map, randomly generated characters<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928090/extras/267f1db6535c13f41009539bf4e0d212.avif?t=1743991103\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928090/extras/d49a582021167bc9245866c59c73e468.poster.avif?t=1743991103\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928090/extras/d49a582021167bc9245866c59c73e468.webm?t